<inglise> (a) A new point 4a is added: </inglise>
<eesti> a) Lisatakse punkt 4a: </eesti>
<inglise> "4a. </inglise>
<eesti> "4a. </eesti>
<inglise> With the prior agreement of the Commission and in the case of co-financed measures only, where a large number of small payments must be made, payments to applicants for aid may be delegated to other bodies. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui kaasrahastatavate meetmete puhul tuleb teha palju v&auml;ikesi makseid, v&otilde;ib komisjoni eelneval n&otilde;usolekul delegeerida abi taotlejatele tehtavad maksed teistele organitele. </eesti>
<inglise> A written agreement must be concluded between the paying agency and that body specifying the nature of the information and the supporting documents to be submitted to the paying agency and the time limit within which they must be submitted; they must as a minimum permit the paying agency to comply with the accreditation criteria and to meet the deadlines laid down for the submission of monthly and annual accounts. </inglise>
<eesti> Makseasutus ja k&otilde;nealune organ peavad s&otilde;lmima kirjaliku kokkuleppe, milles m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks makseasutusele esitatava teabe laad ja t&otilde;endavad dokumendid ning nende esitamise t&auml;htaeg; makseasutus peab saama nende andmete ja dokumentide abil t&auml;ita v&auml;hemalt volitamiskriteeriume ning j&auml;rgida kuu- ja aastaaruannete esitamise t&auml;htaegu. </eesti>
<inglise> The paying agency shall remain responsible for the efficient management of the funds concerned and for updating accounting records. </inglise>
<eesti> Makseasutus vastutab asjakohaste rahaliste vahendite t&otilde;husa juhtimise ning raamatupidamisdokumentide ajakohastamise eest. </eesti>
<inglise> The authorised agents of the paying agency, the certifying body and the European Union shall have the right to examine any evidence held by the abovementioned body and to carry out checks on applicants for aid." </inglise>
<eesti> Makseasutuse, t&otilde;endeid v&auml;ljastava organi ja Euroopa Liidu volitatud esindajatel on &otilde;igus uurida k&otilde;iki eespool nimetatud organi k&auml;sutuses olevaid t&otilde;endeid ja kontrollida abi taotlejaid." </eesti>
<inglise> (b) The following is added to point 5: </inglise>
<eesti> b) Punktile 5 lisatakse j&auml;rgmine tekst: </eesti>
<inglise> "The administrative subunit responsible for the execution of the payments, or else a unit responsible for supervising it, shall have available documentary evidence of the authorisation of claims, and of the administrative and physical checks prescribed. </inglise>
<eesti> "Maksete tegemise eest vastutaval haldus&uuml;ksusel v&otilde;i k&otilde;nealuse &uuml;ksuse j&auml;relevalve&uuml;ksusel peab olema v&otilde;imalus kasutada dokumentaalseid t&otilde;endeid n&otilde;uete heakskiitmise kohta ning etten&auml;htud haldus- ja f&uuml;&uuml;silise kontrolli kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> The information and the evidence may be in a summary form equivalent to that described in point 4(iv) of this Annex, and it may be provided through a computerised system." </inglise>
<eesti> Teabe ja t&otilde;endid v&otilde;ib esitada k&auml;esoleva lisa punkti 4 alapunktis iv kirjeldatud kokkuv&otilde;tlikus vormis ja need v&otilde;ib saata elektroonilisel kujul." </eesti>
<inglise> (c) The following sentence is added to the second subparagraph of point 6(ii): </inglise>
<eesti> c) Punkti 6 alapunkti ii teisele l&otilde;igule lisatakse j&auml;rgmine tekst: </eesti>
<inglise> "Appropriate measures must be taken to avoid a conflict of interests where a person occupying a position of responsibility or a sensitive position with regard to the verification, authorisation and payment of claims on the Fund also fulfils other functions outside the paying agency." </inglise>
<eesti> "Tuleb v&otilde;tta asjakohaseid meetmeid, et v&auml;ltida huvide konflikti juhul, kui vastutaval v&otilde;i strateegilisel ametikohal t&ouml;&ouml;tav isik, kes tegeleb fondile esitatud n&otilde;uete kontrollimise, heakskiitmise ja v&auml;ljamaksmisega, t&auml;idab v&auml;ljaspool makseasutust ka muid &uuml;lesandeid." </eesti>
